Ikirwa cya malahide giherereye mukiyaga cya Kivu Muburengerazuba bw'[[U Rwanda|urwanda]] , iki kirwa ni kimwe mubirwa byiza [[File:An aerial of Paradis Malahide island in Lake Kivu with the area of 2,700 km². Emmanuel Kwizera.jpg|thumb|An aerial of Paradis Malahide island in Lake Kivu with the area of 2,700 km². Emmanuel Kwizera]]

biri mukiyaga cya Kivu<ref>https://www.expertafrica.com/rwanda/lake-kivu/in-detail</ref> Iki Kirwa giherereye mucyaro gitoya cy'Urwanda ahitwa Irubona Mubirometero 7km uvuye mumugi wa [[Umujyi wa Rubavu|Gisenyi]] kandi ikaba munkengero zikiyaga cya [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|Kivu]] mukarere ka [[Umujyi wa Rubavu|Rubavu]] .

